transcript_parts.text: hi this is Paul just wanted to make a

he's the pastor of the Alameda Christian
Reformed Church and he's graciously
offered to have his building used for
that purposes that his buildings the
church is building but I will be there
with a few people from the Sacramento
Meetup and I know there's some people

there so a new Meetup July 14 kickoff
for p.m. Alameda Christian Reformed
Church you can go to meetup.com and just
